
This schematic has sereval options : for the LiPo charger you have the choice between use indivitual components or use a ready to go LiPo charger.

They KEY feature of the sensor is the "DeepSleep" jumper : This juster has to be set ONLY after final programming because is uses the RESET Pin also used by programmation.
One the sowgware is uploaded, solder this jumper in order to link the IO16 timer with the RESET Pin
